msgstr "**Parte del discurso** (sustantivo, verbo, adjetivo, etc.)"

#: ../../4-Language 0628e4c3eae342d8ae1cf38341e3e8d2 data.rst:24
msgid ""
"**Named entities** (Person, location, personally identifiable "
